{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1c153ad2e3","title":"在林枫家属来信摘要上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2107bbab92","index":0,"year":1972,"month":8,"day":11,"articleId":"1c153ad2e3"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"451d61da15","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"汪，指汪东兴，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"89764bd9d1","type":"title","text":"在林枫家属来信摘要上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3"},{"id":"451d61da15","type":"paragraph","text":"连原信一起，请注回印发政治局客同志。我意放他出来治病林枫问题过去没有弄清楚，有些证据不足，办案人员似有一些逼供信。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3"},{"id":"23c85e1e59","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3"},{"id":"5a07978f89","type":"paragraph","text":"七二年八月十一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3"},{"id":"62fe235565","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这个批语写在中共中央办公厅信访处1972年8月10日编印的《来信摘要》第五四五号上。来信摘要写道，原中共中央高级党校校长林枫的子女林梅梅等8月5日写信给毛主席，说他们8月4日去秦城见了林枫一面，林现惠心脏病、糖尿病，神情呆带，身体枯瘦，请求让他出来治疗休养。1973年7月7日，林枫给毛泽东写信说：“在您和中央的亲切关怀下，我到阜外医院治病已经十个多月了。”信中请求早日恢复他的党组织生活，还揭发了林彪在东北的几个问题。7月10日，毛泽东阅信后批示：“纪、汪韵处。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3"}],"page":{"id":"a6b5af9af5","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"1c153ad2e3","start":330,"end":330}}}},"__N_SSG":true}